  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/394",
  "title": "Inconsistency between facet widgets for hasResults",
  "body": "We sometimes use `facetValues.length`, some others `nbHits` (or even `hits.length`, leading to even more inconsistency).\nI think we should:\n- either rename `hideContainerWhenNoResults` to `hideContainerWhenNoRefinements` for them and use `facetValues`\n- or expose both, with `hideContainerWhenNoRefinements = false` and `hideContainerWhenNoResults = true`\n\nWDYT?\n",
